      "widgets_values": [
        "md_content = \"\"\"# 🦦 StarNodes Upscaler Models - Download Guide\n\nWelcome to the official model download guide for the **Star Tiled PiD Upscaler** and **Star Tiled SeedVR Upscaler** nodes. \n\nEnsure all models are placed in their respective directories within your ComfyUI installation to keep everything running smoothly. The links below point to the Comfy-Org Hugging Face repositories.\n\n---\n\n## 📥 1. Star Tiled PiD Upscaler\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `pid_1.5_flux2_1024_to_4096_4step_bf16.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/pid_1.5_flux2/resolve/main/diffusion_models/pid_1.5_flux2_1024_to_4096_4step_bf16.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### Text Encoder (CLIP)\n* **File:** `gemma_2_2b_it_elm_fp8_scaled.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/gemma_2/resolve/main/text_encoders/gemma_2_2b_it_elm_fp8_scaled.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/` *(Note: depending on your setup, this may also go into `ComfyUI/models/clip/`)*\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `flux2-vae.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux2/resolve/main/vae/flux2-vae.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n---\n\n## 📥 2. Star Tiled SeedVR Upscaler\n\n### Diffusion Model\n* **File:** `seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/seedvr2/resolve/main/diffusion_models/seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`\n\n### VAE\n* **File:** `ema_vae_fp16.safetensors`\n* **Download:** [HuggingFace / Comfy-Org](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/ema_vae/resolve/main/vae/ema_vae_fp16.safetensors)\n* **Location:** `ComfyUI/models/vae/`\n\n---\n\n## 📂 Folder Structure Overview\n\nDouble-check your `models` directory to ensure everything is structured correctly for the custom nodes:\n\n```text\nComfyUI/\n├── models/\n│   ├── diffusion_models/\n│   │   ├── pid_1.5_flux2_1024_to_4096_4step_bf16.safetensors\n│   │   └── seedvr2_7b-int8_convrot.safetensors\n│   ├── text_encoders/\n│   │   └── gemma_2_2b_it_elm_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n│   └── vae/\n│       ├── flux2-vae.safetensors\n│       └── ema_vae_fp16.safetensors"
      ],
